                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5460" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0819</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8468 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京文化业绩变脸迷局——“商誉暴雷”之殇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The sudden change of Beijing JingxiCulture &amp;Tourism Corporation achievements——Impairment of goodwill</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱清香，李梦亚，梁娜，肖萁杉，李小青，许楠</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京京西文化旅游股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京文化；商誉减值；并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Beijing Culture; Impairment of goodwill; merger</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013年国家正式开放并购，许多影视公司就此开启了并购转型之旅，北京文化也是其中一员。北京文化作为一家半路转型的影视公司，自从2014年从旅游公司转型为影视公司以来，曾陆续发行过《战狼2》、《我不是药神》等优秀电影，优秀的投资眼光让它从“新人”一跃成为影视行业的优秀公司，交出了一份非常满分答卷。然而从2016年之后，由于盲目并购，影视公司的商誉暴雷事件开始频繁发生，北京文化也不能幸免。2019年，北京文化突发23亿元的巨额亏损，根据披露，主要是因为对它名下的两家全资子公司——世纪伙伴和星河文化分别计提了8.34亿和6.41亿的商誉减值。本案例主要描述了北京文化并购和商誉暴雷的全过程，引导学生了解北京文化的并购动因、业绩承诺的定义，掌握商誉的确认以及后续计量方法等。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since its transformation from a tourism company to a film and television company in 2014, Beijing culture has released such excellent films as &quot;war wolf 2&quot; and &quot;I&#39;m not the God of medicine&quot;. Its excellent investment vision has made it become an excellent company in the film and television industry. However, in 2019, Beijing culture suddenly suffered a huge loss of 2.3 billion yuan, This is mainly due to the provision of goodwill impairment of 834 million and 641 million respectively for its two wholly-owned subsidiaries, Century Partner and Xinghe culture. This case mainly describes the whole process of the thunder storm event of Beijing JingxiCulture &amp;Tourism Corporation goodwill. It guides students to understand the motivation of merger and acquisition, the definition of performance commitment, the recognition of goodwill and subsequent measurement methods of Beijing JingxiCulture&amp;Tourism Corporation, so as to provide reference for other companies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《高级财务会计》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购、商誉减值</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
